nearly-6-million-new-subscribers-amid-password-sharing-crackdown-204411234.html">反对帐户共享</a>，并表示该公司“正在积极探索解决帐户共享问题的方法，以及付费订阅者与朋友和家人共享帐户的最佳选择”。该公司预计将于 2024 年某个时候开始实施这些新政策。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/disney-is-raise-prices-and-cracking-down-on-account-sharing-001637934.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/disney-is-raising-prices-and-cracking-down-on-account-sharing-001637934.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> aca845d1-7bd4-4376-813d-8b2e8be168d1</guid><dc:creator>肖恩·巴克利</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 10 Aug 2023 00:16:37 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691626597</ingested><modified> 2023-08-10T00:16:44+00:00</modified><category><![CDATA[Professional Services]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sean Buckley]]></category><media:content height="2071" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-12/04b2d630-3bc4-11eb-bab7-48acdb07d74f" width="3213"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2071" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-12/04b2d630-3bc4-11eb-bab7-48acdb07d74f" width="3213"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[FILE - In this Aug. 13, 2020 file photo, the logos for Netflix, Hulu, Disney Plus and Sling TV are pic