3n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-us-government-is-trying-to-force-bytedance-to-sell-tiktok-005751763.html"><ins>字节跳动施压</ins></a>，要求其出售这款受欢迎的应用程序。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/biden-signs-executive-order-restricting-investment-in-chinese-tech-companies-230728855.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/biden-signs-executive-order-restricting-investment-in-chinese-tech-companies-230728855.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ee495673-2156-43a5-8a84-6d7651727ae1</guid><dc:creator>卡丽莎·贝尔</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 23:07:28 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691622449</ingested><modified> 2023-08-09T23:07:34+00:00</modified><category><![CDATA[Government]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Karissa Bell]]></category><media:content height="3498" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/2ad3be50-3708-11ee-a6fb-f495aaa2625a" width="5248"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3498" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/2ad3be50-3708-11ee-a6fb-f495aaa2625a" width="5248"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[FILE - A podium stands in the James Brady Press Briefing Room of the White House, Sunday, March 22, 2020, in Washington. With roughly a year and a half until the 2024 presidential contest, the field of candidates is largely set. Former President Donald Trump and Florida Gov. Ron DeSantis have dominated the early Republican race, but other candidates including former Vice President Mike Pence, former United Nations Ambassador Nikki Haley and U.S. Sen. Tim Scott of South Carolina are looking for an opening in case either falters. President Joe Biden faces a couple of Democratic challengers but is expected to secure his party’s nomination. (AP Photo/Patrick Semansky, File)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Election 2024 Meet The Candidates]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Threads now lets you share posts directly to Instagram DMs]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>当埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk） <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/elon-musk-says-he-might-need-surgery-before-any-cage-fight-with-mark-zuckerberg-154237731.html">等待医生允许</a>与马克·扎克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）进行一场时断时续的<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/get-ready-for-a-zuck-vs-musk-cage-fight-100611527.html">笼式比赛</a>时，两位亿万富翁的公司继续在消费者采用领域展开争论。今天，Meta 继续推进 Threads 积极的更新计划，试图挑战马斯克不稳定的 X（ <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitters-rebrand-to-x-could-worsen-its-legal-and-financial-problems-233914973.html">更名为 Twitter</a> ）。扎克伯格今天<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.threads.net/@zuck/">宣布</a>，这个年轻的平台现在支持向 Instagram 私信分享帖子、照片和视频的自定义替代文本以及新的提及按钮。</p><p>通过“在 Instagram 上发送”选项，用户可以通过“发送”按钮将他们的主题帖子直接发布到 Instagram DM。据<em>路透社</em>报道，首席产品官 Chris Cox 在最近的一次公司会议上<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/meta-plans-retention-hooks-threads-more-than-half-users-leave-app-2023-07-28/">表示</a>，该功能可以被视为 Meta 精心设计的“保留驱动钩子”之一，以确保“Instagram 应用程序上的用户可以看到重要的线程”。据称，该策略与有关该新兴平台在不到一周内<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/metas-threads-races-to-100-million-users-in-under-a-week-070740016.html">增加了 1 亿多用户</a>后<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/threads-users-are-already-spending-less-time-in-the-app-182738755.html">参与度下降的报道</a>有关。据报道，扎克伯格将这种下降描述为“正常”，并且随着 Meta 继续充实 7 月初<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/metas-instagram-linked-twitter-rival-threads-could-arrive-on-july-6th-063129168.html">推出的</a>社交渠道，预计保留率将会增长。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/cbfb09c0-36ed-11ee-9fff-6c4db0ec6a33" style="height:1080px;width:1800px;" alt="显示 Meta Threads 应用程序的新替代文本功能的三个屏幕截图。左：图像，中：空白替代文本，右：起草替代文本。" data-uuid="c5cb7773-e663-3dc8-a714-d34e578bfce3"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">元</div></figure><p>同时，自定义替代文本选项是一项辅助功能，允许 Threads 用户在上传之前为照片和视频添加（或编辑现有的自动生成的）替代文本。新的提及按钮使您可以更轻松地在 Threads 帖子中标记个人资料。最后，该平台使您可以更轻松地在 Mastodon 等联邦平台上验证您的身份。 Instagram 负责人 Adam Mosseri 今天<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.threads.net/@mosseri/post/Cvu2fDiLZve">发帖称</a>：“您现在可以在支持的平台上添加您的 Threads 个人资料链接来验证您的身份。”</p><p>这些只是 Meta 在过去几周推出的最新功能。该公司本月早些时候宣布， <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/threads-is-getting-a-web-version-and-a-search-function-in-the-next-few-weeks-101220107.html">急需的网络版本</a>即将推出，首次提供桌面使用以及适当的搜索功能。其他发布后添加的功能包括<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/threads-adds-a-chronological-feed-as-twitter-burns-to-the-ground-152817251.html">按时间顺序排列的提要</a>以及对<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/first-big-threads-update-for-ios-helps-you-see-new-followers-195035774.html">关注列表进行排序</a>和查看喜欢的帖子的功能。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/threads-now-lets-you-share-posts-directly-to-instagram-dms-201857138.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/threads-now-lets-you-share-posts-directly-to-instagram-dms-201857138.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> cd00ce46-93ba-4001-9566-d41