gamedeveloper.com/business/translators-and-external-developers-reportedly-missing-from-baldurs-gate-3-credits"><ins>据</ins><em><ins>《游戏开发者》报道，该游戏似乎未能归功于许多帮助完成该项目的工作人员。</ins></em></a></p><p>这个问题最初是由<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/katrinaltrnsl8r/status/1688948162269261824"><ins>自由本地化制作人 Katrina Leonoudakis</ins></a>发现的，她指出游戏的制作人员名单中没有提及从事巴西和葡萄牙语本地化工作的译者。一家名为 Altagram Group 的公司负责这些翻译，值得注意的是公司高管和部门领导出现在片尾字幕中。此外，本地化为其他语言（例如意大利语）的翻译人员也得到了适当的认可，尽管这些翻译是由 Altagram 以外的公司处理的。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>这个问题不仅仅限于翻译人员，因为<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/Fl4ky/status/1688212637933518848"><ins>报告还表明</ins></a>外包工作室未能列出参与该项目的许多开发人员。制作人员名单列出了每个工作室的名字，但没有列出参与游戏的具体员工。</p><p>就其本身而言，拉​​里安处于领先地位。该公司在<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.eurogamer.net/baldurs-gate-3-developer-demands-full-list-of-uncredited-translation-staff-immediately"><ins>向</ins><em><ins>Eurogamer</ins></em>提供的一份声明中指出，“这都是 Altagram 集团造成的”，并且“迫使他们解决这个问题” <ins>。</ins></a>开发人员接着说修复即将到来。</p><p>开发人员正在努力解决这个问题绝对是一件好事，因为人们的工作值得赞扬。然而，这已成为游戏行业中非常普遍的做法。<em>游戏开发者</em>与几位本地化专家进行了交谈，他们描述了在正确评价承包商时采取的“自由放任”态度。为此，在过去一年中出现了多次这种做法的例子，从<em>《女神异闻录 3》</em>和《女神异<em>闻录 4》</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://kotaku.com/persona-localisation-translation-credits-sega-3-4-1850017066"><ins>的翻译人员</ins></a>没有得到适当的认可，到《 <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.gamedeveloper.com/business/mercurysteam-defends-its-leaving-developers-out-of-metroid-dread-credits"><em><ins>银河战士恐惧》</ins></em></a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.gamedeveloper.com/business/god-of-war-ragnarok-dev-claims-they-weren-t-credited-for-their-work-on-the-game"><em><ins>《战争之神：诸神黄昏》</ins></em></a>等知名游戏的艺术家和开发商没有得到适当的认可。他们闪耀的时刻。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/baldurs-gate-3-credits-are-missing-a-bunch-of-outsourced-workers-183726183.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/baldurs-gate-3-credits-are-missing-a-bunch-of-outsourced-workers-183726183.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 3b3cf88a-15e6-40fc-a52e-c94b245078f7</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 18:37:26 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691606247</ingested><modified> 2023-08-09T18:37:36+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="1209" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/0e07f960-36dd-11ee-a5f9-7aa8eacce350" width="2056"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1209" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/0e07f960-36dd-11ee-a5f9-7aa8eacce350" width="2056"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Larian Studios ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Screenshot from 'Baldur's Gate III' featuring a party of adventurers.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Baldur's Gate III]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Cadillac’s first Escalade EV has a 450-mile range and starts at $130,000]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>凯迪拉克今天<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://media.cadillac.com/media/us/en/cadillac/home.detail.html/content/Pages/news/us/en/2023/aug/0809-escaladeiq.html">发布了</a>首款全电动凯雷德。 2025 款凯迪拉克 Escalade IQ 是一款售价 13 万美元以上的豪华车型，使用 <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2020-03-04-gm-ultium-ev-batteries.html">通用汽车的 Ultium 电池</a>，可续航 450 英里。但它的价格并不是这款 SUV 唯一令人畏惧的地方：它甚至比标准汽油动力凯雷德更大，而且几乎与长轴距车型<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2021-cadillac-escalade-esv-officially-141800656.html">凯雷德 ESV</a>一样长。然而，凯迪拉克表示，它仍然“被认为是通用汽车有史以来生产的最符合空气动力学的全尺寸 SUV”。</p><p> SUV 配备 24 模块 Ultium 电池，可产生超过 200kWh 的可用能量。它支持 800 伏直流快速充电，在 350 千瓦直流充电站充电 10 分钟可提供长达 100 英里的续航里程。它支持高达 19.2 kW 的交流电，每小时充电预计可行驶 37 英里。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> Escalade IQ 有两个电动机，在正常模式下可提供 680 马力（505 kW）和 615 磅英尺（834 牛米）的扭矩。然而，在速度最大模式下，它可以达到 750 马力（560 千瓦）和 785 磅英尺（1,064 牛米）。在 Velocity Max 模式下，预计可在 5 秒内达到 60 英里/小时。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/caf3b440-36df-11ee-9fcf-a3f054802b5f" style="height:1200px;width:2000px;" alt="2025 款凯迪拉克 Escalade IQ 的中控台视图。它有棕色真皮座椅和仪表板上的 55 英寸双屏 LED 显示屏。日光下，透过挡风玻璃可以看到城市建筑。" data-uuid="dc403ff0-442f-38c8-a0dd-546a3f31cf77"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">卡迪拉克</div></figure><p>Escalade IQ 将在公路上亮相，加入<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/hummer-ev-first-drive-an-enormous-electric-super-truck-133030316.html">悍马</a>、 <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/chevrolet-silverado-ev-details-ces-debut-171551300.html">Silverado</a> 、 <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gm-officially-reveals-its-electrified-2024-gmc-sierra-denali-213601650.html">GMC Sierra Denali</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/stellantis-first-look-ram-1500-revolution-bev-concept-ces-2023-223035895.html">Ram 1500 EV</a>等电动庞然大物的行列。新款凯迪拉克长近 19 英尺，宽 8 英尺，高超过 6 英尺。但当第二排和第三排座椅折叠起来时，你的车内空间很大，载货量为 119.2 立方英尺。 （它还有一个后备箱，可额外增加 12 立方英尺的存储空间。）</p><p>总而言之，这款 SUV 的牵引力可达 8,000 磅。此外，它还配备了跨仪表板的 55 英寸双屏 LED 显示屏，其信息娱乐系统运行 Android Automotive OS（包括 Google Assistant、Google 地图和 Play 商店）。高端系列通过 AKG 40 扬声器阵列提供 360 度音频。</p><p> 2025 款 Escalade IQ 将于明年夏天在通用汽车位于底特律的零工厂装配中心开始生产。定价“起价约为 130,000 美元”，包括目的地费用。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/cadillacs-first-escalade-ev-has-a-450-mile-range-and-starts-at-130000-182816273.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/cadillacs-first-escalade-ev-has-a-450-mile-range-and-starts-at-130000-182816273.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f72406eb-802b-43fa-8325-6a3c5e10841a</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 18:28:16 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691609780</ingested><modified> 2023-08-09T19:36:30+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="1072" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/e8aa8730-36e3-11ee-bf57-8d0734062ab4" width="1859"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1072" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/e8aa8730-36e3-11ee-bf57-8d0734062ab4" width="1859"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Cadillac]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Marketing photo for the 2025 Cadillac Escalade IQ. The silver SUV sits on a city street in front of brownstone buildings with skyscrapers in the background.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[2025 Cadillac Escalade IQ]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Epic loses bid to make Apple change its App Store payment rules right now]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/epic-games/"><ins>Epic Games</ins></a>试图迫使<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/apple/"><ins>苹果</ins></a>尽快改变其 App Store 支付方式，但失败了。这家<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/fortnite/"><em><ins>《堡垒之夜》</ins></em></a>制造商要求最高法院推翻美国第九巡回上诉法院的一项裁决，该裁决推迟了针对苹果应用商店规则的禁令。然而，据<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://news.bloomberglaw.com/us-law-week/apple-can-keep-app-store-rules-for-now-as-top-court-spurns-epic"><em><ins>彭博社</ins></em></a>报道，埃琳娜·卡根法官<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.supremecourt.gov/search.aspx?filename=/docket/docketfiles/html/public/23a78.html"><ins>拒绝了这一请求</ins></a>，没有提供任何解释<em>&nbsp;</em>报告。</p><p>第九巡回上诉法院最初于四月份<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-wins-appeals-court-ruling-against-epic-games-191331514.html"><ins>维持了该禁令</ins></a>。然而，它于 7 月暂停了该禁令，以便苹果可以<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-wants-to-take-the-epic-games-case-to-the-supreme-court-123501115.html"><ins>将此案提交至最高法院</ins></a>。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>在 2021 年苹果和 Epic Games 进行了一场轰动一时的审判后，一名下级法院法官<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-epic-games-lawsuit-ruling-app-store-153113436.html"><ins>裁定</ins></a>，苹果阻止第三方开发商引导用户选择其他支付选项，违反了加州的不公平竞争法。法官下令停止这种做法。</p><p>过去三年来，两家公司一直在 iOS 上的应用内支付问题上争论不休。 Epic 告诉移动<em>《堡垒之夜</em>》玩家，如果<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/epic-games-fortnite-direct-payment-discounts-143422257.html"><ins>绕过 iOS 和 Android 支付系统，</ins></a>他们将获得游戏内 V-Bucks 货币的折扣，这引起了苹果（和谷歌）的愤怒。苹果和谷歌在 iOS 和 Android 上的应用内交易<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-small-business-program-15-percent-112259064.html"><ins>中抽取了 30% 的分成</ins></a>。</p><p>移动平台持有者迅速将<em>《堡垒之夜》</em>从各自的应用商店下架，Epic 对<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/fortnite-google-play-lawsuit-035741548.html"><ins>他们</ins></a><a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/fortnite-maker-epic-games-sues-apple-195415590.html"><ins>提起诉讼</ins></a>，法律诉讼仍在继续。 Google 案件（<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/match-group-sues-google-225719753.html"><ins>Match Group</ins></a>作为原告参与其中）将于今年 11 月<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/epic-match-google-antitrust-lawsuit-trial-date-223014942.html#:~:text=Both%20Epic%20and%20Match%20accuse,demanding%20%244.7%20billion%20in%20damages."><ins>开庭审理</ins></a>。</p><p>无论美国发生什么，苹果和谷歌已经被迫在某些市场（例如<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-now-allows-third-party-payments-for-apps-in-south-korea-120524308.html"><ins>韩国</ins></a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-tweaks-third-party-dating-app-payment-dutch-regulators-order-155145831.html"><ins>荷兰）</ins></a>向第三方支付系统开放其平台。另据报道，苹果计划<a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-third-party-app-stores-report-195840839.html"><ins>最快明年</ins></a>在 iPhone 上允许第三方应用商店，这在很大程度上是为了遵守即将出台的欧盟规则。 Epic 已经为此做好了准备，因为它自己的移动应用商店已<a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.axios.com/2023/03/09/epic-games-store-tim-sweeney-2023">准备就绪</a>。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/epic-loses-bid-to-make-apple-change-its-app-store- payment-rules-right-now-174924222.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/epic-loses-bid-to-make-apple-change-its-app-store-payment-rules-right-now-174924222.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> a6623aaf-8957-42e4-9f3e-701ebc830b1e</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 17:49:24 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691603366</ingested><modified> 2023-08-09T17:49:48+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Company Legal & Law Matters]]></category><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Mobile Apps]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="2184" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-04/f83f5a40-a7b6-11eb-b97f-1ec9ee0319dd" width="3312"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2184" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-04/f83f5a40-a7b6-11eb-b97f-1ec9ee0319dd" width="3312"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[FILE - This March 19, 2018 file photo shows Apple's App Store app. Epic Games said Wednesday Feb. 17, 2021, it filed an antitrust complaint against Apple with European Union regulators, opening up a new front in its war with the tech giant over app store payments. (AP Photo/Patrick Semansky, File)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Europe Epic Games Apple]]></media:title></media:content></item></channel></rss>